                            <comment id="14409" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Sun, 21 Aug 2005 19:41:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;While this is not really intended usage of the &quot;parentMessageSource&quot; / &quot;parentThemeSource&quot; property (they are mainly intended for being set by the context), I don&apos;t see any issues with adding such a check. Hence, both HierarchicalMessageSource and HierarchicalThemeSource are checked for an existing parent first now, before the parent reference gets overwritten by the context.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Juergen&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
